t types</h5><div _ngcontent-nyo-c9="" class="form-group radio-group-form row"><!----><div _ngcontent-nyo-c9="" class="doc-types-radio col-lg-6 col-md-12"><input _ngcontent-nyo-c9="" name="radio" type="radio" id="PP" class="ng-untouched ng-pristine ng-valid"><label _ngcontent-nyo-c9="" class="radio-label main-doc-types" for="PP">Ordinary 34 pages</label></div><div _ngcontent-nyo-c9="" class="doc-types-radio col-lg-6 col-md-12"><input _ngcontent-nyo-c9="" name="radio" type="radio" id="PB" class="ng-untouched ng-pristine ng-valid"><label _ngcontent-nyo-c9="" class="radio-label main-doc-types" for="PB">Ordinary 66 pages</label></div></div><div _ngcontent-nyo-c9="" aria-multiselectable="true" class="faq-accordion" id="accordionEx" role="tablist"><div _ngcontent-nyo-c9=""><div _ngcontent-nyo-c9="" id="headingOne" role="tab"><a _ngcontent-nyo-c9="" aria-controls="collapseOne" aria-expanded="false" class="collapsed" data-parent="#accordionEx" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapseOne"><h4 _ngcontent-nyo-c9="" class="otherOptions"><i _ngcontent-nyo-c9="" class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i><i _ngcontent-nyo-c9="" class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i> Other Passport Types</h4></a></div><div _ngcontent-nyo-c9="" aria-labelledby="headingOne" class="collapse" data-parent="#accordionEx" id="collapseOne" role="tabpanel"><div _ngcontent-nyo-c9="" class="form-group radio-group-form row"><!----><div _ngcontent-nyo-c9="" class="doc-types-radio col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-sm-6"><input _ngcontent-nyo-c9="" name="radio" type="radio" id="PS" class="ng-untouched ng-pristine ng-valid"><label _ngcontent-nyo-c9="" class="radio-label main-doc-types" for="PS">Service</label></div><div _ngcontent-nyo-c9="" class="doc-types-radio col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-sm-6"><input _ngcontent-nyo-c9="" name="radio" type="radio" id="PD" class="ng-untouched ng-pristine ng-valid"><label _ngcontent-nyo-c9="" class="radio-label main-doc-types" for="PD">Diplomatic</label></div><div _ngcontent-nyo-c9="" class="doc-types-radio col-lg-4